{"content":"<header class=\"shadow-md sm:p-2 w-full bg-white dark:text-white dark:bg-navy mb-20\"><div class=\"flex justify-between\"><a class=\"justify-self-start self-center m-3 ml-5 text-md sm:text-2xl\" href=\"en-US/\">Perseus</a><div class=\"xs:hidden m-3 mr-5 tham tham-e-spin tham-w-6 \"><div class=\"tham-box\"><div class=\"dark:bg-white tham-inner\"></div></div></div><nav class=\"hidden xs:flex\"><ul class=\"mr-5 flex\"><li class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a href=\"en-US/docs\" class=\"px-2\">Docs</a></li><li class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a class=\"px-2\" href=\"en-US/comparisons\">Comparisons</a></li><li class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a href=\"en-US/plugins\" class=\"px-2\">Plugins</a></li></ul></nav></div><nav class=\"xs:hidden w-full text-center justify-center hidden\" id=\"mobile_nav_menu\"><ul class=\"mr-5\"><li class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a href=\"en-US/docs\" class=\"px-2\">Docs</a></li><li class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a href=\"en-US/comparisons\" class=\"px-2\">Comparisons</a></li><li class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a class=\"px-2\" href=\"en-US/plugins\">Plugins</a></li></ul></nav></header><div class=\"overflow-y-scroll\"><main class=\"h-full\"><div class=\"bg-cover h-full flex justify-center items-center text-center dark:text-white\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;.perseus/static/svg/splash_page_bg.svg&quot;), url(&quot;.perseus/static/svg/polygon_scatter.svg&quot;);\"><div><p class=\"text-7xl xs:text-8xl sm:text-9xl p-2 font-extrabold\">Perseus</p><p class=\"text-lg\">The Rust framework for the modern web.</p><br/><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center\"><a href=\"en-US/docs\" class=\"py-3 px-4 m-2 font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-2xl text-white bg-indigo-500 hover:bg-indigo-400 transition-colors duration-200\">Get Started</a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center py-2 px-4 m-2 font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-2xl dark:text-white ring-4 ring-indigo-500 hover:ring-indigo-400 transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"https://github.com/arctic-hen7/perseus\"><span class=\"mr-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 17 16\" fill=\"none\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\"><g clip-path=\"url(githublogo)\" class=\"jsx-120409797\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.18391.249268C3.82241.249268.253906 3.81777.253906 8.17927c0 3.46933 2.279874 6.44313 5.451874 7.53353.3965.0991.49563-.1983.49563-.3965v-1.3878c-2.18075.4956-2.67638-.9912-2.67638-.9912-.3965-.8922-.89212-1.1895-.89212-1.1895-.69388-.4957.09912-.4957.09912-.4957.793.0992 1.1895.793 1.1895.793.69388 1.2887 1.88338.8922 2.27988.6939.09912-.4956.29737-.8921.49562-1.0904-1.78425-.1982-3.5685-.8921-3.5685-3.96496 0-.89212.29738-1.586.793-2.08162-.09912-.19825-.3965-.99125.09913-2.08163 0 0 .69387-.19825 2.18075.793.59475-.19825 1.28862-.29737 1.9825-.29737.69387 0 1.38775.09912 1.98249.29737 1.4869-.99125 2.1808-.793 2.1808-.793.3965 1.09038.1982 1.88338.0991 2.08163.4956.59475.793 1.28862.793 2.08162 0 3.07286-1.8834 3.66766-3.66764 3.86586.29737.3965.59474.8921.59474 1.586v2.1808c0 .1982.0991.4956.5948.3965 3.172-1.0904 5.4518-4.0642 5.4518-7.53353-.0991-4.3615-3.6676-7.930002-8.02909-7.930002z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" class=\"jsx-120409797\"></path></g><defs class=\"jsx-120409797\"><clipPath id=\"githublogo\" class=\"jsx-120409797\"><path fill=\"transparent\" d=\"M0 0h15.86v15.86H0z\" transform=\"translate(.253906 .0493164)\"></path></clipPath></defs></svg></span><span> GitHub</span></a></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-cover py-4 text-white\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;.perseus/static/svg/stacked_waves.svg&quot;);\"><div class=\"flex justify-center text-center text-lg w-full\"><p class=\"p-1 xs:p-4 max-w-7xl\">Perseus is a web development framework built entirely in Rust, designed to empower efficient development of the next generation of lightning-fast sites for the modern web. It comes with server-side rendering, static site generation, internationalization, and inferred routing built-in, letting you build even the most complex sites in a breeze.</p></div><br/><div class=\"flex justify-center\"><ul class=\"text-center max-w-7xl mx-2\"><li class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Static generation</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\">Pre-render pages at build-time before you've even had any visits!</p></div></li><li class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Server-side rendering</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\">Render pages on the server to reduce the load on the client.</p></div></li><li class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Internationalization</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\">Out-of-the-box support for building your app in multiple languages.</p></div></li><li class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Incremental generation</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\">Render pages on-demand and cache them for future use.</p></div></li><li class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Revalidation</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\">Rebuild pages automatically without lifting a finger.</p></div></li><li class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">CLI</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\">Comes with a friendly interface to accelerate your development pace.</p></div></li><li class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Inferred routing</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\">You do your app, Perseus does the rest automatically.</p></div></li><li class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">App shell</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\">Get all the benefits of a single-page app without any of the downsides.</p></div></li><li class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Single-command deployment</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\">Take your apps to production with one command.</p></div></li><li class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Static exporting</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\">Deploy your apps without needing a server.</p></div></li></ul></div><br/><br/><div class=\"flex justify-center text-center text-lg w-full p-1 xs:p-4\"><div class=\"p-4 shadow-2xl rounded-xl max-w-lg\"><p class=\"underline text-2xl mb-2\">Building a Perseus App:</p><ol class=\"list-decimal list-inside\"><li><span>Install Perseus: <code>cargo install perseus-cli</code></span></li><li><span>Build your awesome app with <a href=\"https://github.com/sycamore-rs/sycamore\" class=\"underline\">Sycamore</a></span></li><li><span>Serve your app locally: <code>perseus serve</code></span></li><li><span>Deploy your app to a single directory: <code>perseus deploy</code></span></li><li><span>Upload that to a server!</span></li></ol></div></div></div><div class=\"pb-24 flex flex-col justify-center text-white\" style=\"background: url(&quot;.perseus/static/svg/cta_bg.svg&quot;);background-size:cover;\"><div class=\"text-3xl 2xs:text-4xl xs:text-5xl sm:text-6xl p-2 font-extrabold text-center\"><p>What are you waiting for?</p><p>Dive in and start building for the web of tomorrow!</p></div><br/><div class=\"flex justify-center\"><a class=\"py-3 px-4 m-2 text-xl font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-2xl text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"en-US/docs\">Get Started</a></div><br/><div class=\"flex justify-center\"><a class=\"py-2 px-4 m-2 font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-2xl text-white bg-indigo-500 hover:bg-indigo-400 transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"en-US/comparisons\">Or See How Perseus Compares</a></div></div></main></div><footer class=\"w-full flex justify-center py-5 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-navy-deep\"><p class=\"dark:text-white mx-5 text-center\"><span>© <a href=\"https://github.com/arctic-hen7\" class=\"underline\">arctic-hen7</a> ⁨2021⁩, see license <a href=\"https://github.com/arctic-hen7/perseus/blob/main/LICENSE\" class=\"underline\">here</a>.</span></p></footer>","state":null,"head":"<title>Perseus</title>"}